{"tid":2426661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★公屋又贏！受惠屯馬線通車，顯徑邨勁賺逾16倍","createTime":"2021-02-28T08:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T08:45:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4056bf2ac70e478ea9947c80ddc0fa851027a9","tid":2426661,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"顯徑邨位於新界東沙田區，鄰近顯徑站及獅子山隧道入口，鄰近亦有指標私樓或新盤如名城及柏傲莊，加上去年通車的港鐵屯馬線設有顯徑站，令顯徑邨一躍而成鐵路沿線屋苑，多個因素令該處成為新界區造價較高租置屋邨。<br />\n<br />\n截至2019年，顯徑邨未出售的單位僅為7.3%，是全港租置屋邨之中最低。根據過往成交紀錄，顯徑邨曾有補價單位轉手賺2倍，而綠表單位<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>更曾錄得勁賺逾16倍的個案</strong></span>，而租置單位價格近年跑贏大巿，甚至出現炒賣情況，着實令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/574482/%E7%A7%9F%E7%BD%AE%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E7%B7%9A%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E9%A1%AF%E5%BE%91%E9%82%A8%E8%AE%8A%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%B2%BF%E7%B7%9A%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91-%E5%83%857-3-%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E6%9C%AA%E5%94%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F574482%2F%25E7%25A7%259F%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2580%259A-%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E5%25BE%2591%25E9%2582%25A8%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%25B2%25BF%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%258B%2591-%25E5%2583%25857-3-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2594%25AE&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3rM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e04962b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/574482/%E7%A7%9F%E7%BD%AE%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%B1%AF%E9%A6%AC%E7%B7%9A%E9%96%8B%E9%80%9A-%E9%A1%AF%E5%BE%91%E9%82%A8%E8%AE%8A%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%B2%BF%E7%B7%9A%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91-%E5%83%857-3-%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E6%9C%AA%E5%94%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210126/430792642524090368156473.jpeg/Y6y-VPo0ej90